java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants, Announcer.StageListener
public class GecoWindow
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements Announcer.StageListener

GecoWindow is the main frame of the application and primarily responsible for initializing the main GecoPanel in tabs. It also takes care of the main toolbar.
